964
01:11:10,327 --> 01:11:14,593
Oh, sure, you look exactly like
that guy in Rain Man.

965
01:11:16,934 --> 01:11:19,767
Oh, yeah? Well, people say
I look like Tom Cruise all the time.

966
01:11:19,870 --> 01:11:21,565
Oh, yeah? No, I'd, uh...

967
01:11:22,673 --> 01:11:26,336
The other one, the... What's his...
Uhhh... The retard.

968
01:11:27,344 --> 01:11:32,577
I just love that scene in Vegas
when the retard wins at blackjack.

969
01:11:33,517 --> 01:11:35,451
You look just like that.

970
01:11:39,323 --> 01:11:46,195
What I could never understand, though,
is how someone so retarded,

971
01:11:47,097 --> 01:11:48,792
could win so much.

972
01:11:51,168 --> 01:11:54,660
Hey, Jeffrey, his brother
from another mother,

973
01:11:54,772 --> 01:11:56,535
how did that retard
win so much?

974
01:11:56,640 --> 01:11:59,575
- You know what, sir? I think that maybe...
