975
01:11:59,676 --> 01:12:01,871
Oh, I didn't mean it.

976
01:12:36,080 --> 01:12:39,277
His luck'll run out eventually.
It always does.

977
01:12:49,660 --> 01:12:51,890
- Hey, Ben...
- No, Ben, stop it!

978
01:12:51,995 --> 01:12:53,860
- What the hell is the matter with you?
- Hey, come on! Ben!

979
01:12:53,964 --> 01:12:57,422
Oh, you think that's funny?
You think that was funny? Shut up!

980
01:12:57,534 --> 01:12:58,899
I understand, Ben.
We don't need any more...

981
01:12:59,002 --> 01:13:00,833
This is not the time. Okay?

982
01:13:00,938 --> 01:13:03,240
I wanna thank you for
confirming my choice in Ben.

983
01:13:03,240 --> 01:13:04,776
- Sure.
- Now, go home.

984
01:13:11,582 --> 01:13:13,573
- What?
- You're off the team.

985
01:13:13,684 --> 01:13:14,742
No.

986
01:13:15,752 --> 01:13:19,119
- I was-I was drunk, I was...
- I don't care what you were.

987
01:13:20,357 --> 01:13:21,654
I'm not leaving.

988
01:13:21,758 --> 01:13:24,283
Yes, you are.

989
01:13:24,795 --> 01:13:27,263
What are you gonna do
about it, huh?

990
01:13:31,135 --> 01:13:35,003
You've been the big man for a long time,
but you just acted like a child.

991
01:13:35,105 --> 01:13:38,233
So, I want you to pick up
the ticket and go home,

992
01:13:38,342 --> 01:13:42,369
because if you don't, you know exactly
what I'm capable of doing,

993
01:13:42,980 --> 01:13:44,277
don't you?

994
01:14:01,532 --> 01:14:02,521
All right, listen up.

995
01:14:02,633 --> 01:14:06,160
Casino's gonna change out their chips,
just like the MGM did after the Tyson fight.

996
01:14:06,270 --> 01:14:09,137
That means we got less
than 24 hours to cash in,

997
01:14:09,239 --> 01:14:11,503
or we're gonna be sitting with
200 grand of worthless plastic.

998
01:14:11,608 --> 01:14:13,838
- So, we'll cash out.
- It's too hot.

999
01:14:13,944 --> 01:14:17,846
